#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"License and source code distribution\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Лицензия и исходный код\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails is [Free Software](https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html): you "
"can download, use, and share it with no restrictions."
msgstr ""
"Tails – [бесплатное программное обеспечение](https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/"
"free-sw.ru.html): вы можете скачивать, использовать и делиться им без каких-"
"либо ограничений."

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The Tails source code is released under the GNU/GPL (version 3 or above) "
#| "and is Copyright (C) Tails developers <info@tails.net>.  Any exception to "
#| "this rule is documented either below or in the affected source file."
msgid ""
"The Tails source code is released under the GNU/GPL (version 3 or above) and "
"is Copyright (C) Tails developers <foundations@tails.net>.  Any exception to "
"this rule is documented either below or in the affected source file."
msgstr ""
"Исходный код Tails публикуется под лицензией GNU/GPL (версии 3 или старше) и "
"защищён авторскими правами (c) разработчиков Tails <info@tails.net>. Всякое "
"исключение из этого правила указано ниже либо описано в соответствующем "
"исходном файле."

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "However, Tails includes non-free firmware in order to work on as much "
#| "hardware as possible."
msgid ""
"However, Tails, like Debian, includes closed source binary firmware in order "
"to work on as much hardware as possible."
msgstr ""
"Однако Tails использует небесплатный программный код для более полной "
"аппаратной совместимости."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails is a registered trademark of The Tor Project, Inc. See our [Trademark "
"and Brand policy](https://www.torproject.org/about/trademark/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Source code"
msgstr "Исходный код"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Most of the software included in Tails is taken directly from upstream "
"Debian packages and is neither modified nor recompiled by Tails."
msgstr ""
"Большая часть программ Tails взята напрямую из пакетов Debian. Разработчики "
"Tails не модифицировали и не перекомпилировали этот код."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The source code of software that is specific to Tails is available in [[our "
"Git repositories|contribute/git]]."
msgstr ""
"Исходный код программ, которые специфичны для Tails, есть в [[наших Git-"
"репозиториях|contribute/git]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The source code of the Debian packages included in Tails is available in the "
"[APT snapshot](https://tagged.snapshots.deb.tails.boum.org/)  that we "
"created for that version of Tails."
msgstr ""
"Исходный код пакетов Debian, включенных в Tails, доступен в [apt-snapshot]"
"(https://tagged.snapshots.deb.tails.boum.org/), который мы создали "
"специально для данной версии Tails."

